main event: A civilian reported observing an unidentified object overhead while sitting on a ranch in Guadaloupe Island.
interesting points: The observation lasted for about 5 minutes,The object was described as circular or elongated, resembling a cigar or missile shape,It was stationary for a time before seeming to increase in speed and disappear,The witness expressed the object did not resemble anything typical they had seen in the sky,The report includes references to previous sightings by the witness within a few years.
witness description: A civilian sitting on a ranch who called attention to the object
